CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1969, pg. 1, reads: "Demand Recognition - Hospital workers at Presbyterian University Hospital give victory salute after confronting administratiors at High Noon. Tuesbay, Dec. 2, and demanding recognition for their organized union Local 1199, Drug and Hospital Employees, RWDSU, ALF-CIO." Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Workers at Presbyterian University Hospital celebrating and making V signs and wearing caps "Local 1199 Drug and Hospital Union" in recognition of union
